}}'''罗博深''' （{{lang-en|Po-shen Loh}}，{{bd|1982年|6月18日}}）是[[卡内基·梅隆大学|卡内基·梅隆大学]]数学[[教授|副教授]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Po-Shen Loh|url=http://www.math.cmu.edu/~ploh/|access-date=2018-02-25|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119213316/https://www.math.cmu.edu/~ploh/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[国际数学奥林匹克|国际数学奥林匹克竞赛]]美国国家队的教练<ref>{{Cite web|title=International Mathematical Olympiad|url=https://www.imo-official.org/team_r.aspx?code=USA&year=2017|website=www.imo-official.org|access-date=2017-12-24|archive-date=2021-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210425072105/http://www.imo-official.org/team_r.aspx?code=USA&year=2017|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.post-gazette.com/local/city/2017/08/14/andrew-gu-allderdice-pittsburgh-public-schools-math-scores-U-S-international-math-olympiad/stories/201708140010|title=More than 300,000 students entered a math contest. The top score came from a 16-year-old in Pittsburgh Public Schools.|last=Sostek|first=Anya|date=2017-08-14|work=[[Pittsburgh_Post-Gazette|Pittsburgh Post-Gazette]]|access-date=2017-12-28|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128024640/https://www.post-gazette.com/local/city/2017/08/14/andrew-gu-allderdice-pittsburgh-public-schools-math-scores-U-S-international-math-olympiad/stories/201708140010|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在他的执教下，美国奥数队在2015年<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.npr.org/2015/07/18/424122249/theyre-no-1-u-s-wins-math-olympiad-for-first-time-in-21-years|title=They're No. 1: U.S. Wins Math Olympiad For First Time In 21 Years|date=2015-07-18|work=[[All_Things_Considered|All Things Considered]]|access-date=2017-12-28|publisher=[[National_Public_Radio|National Public Radio]]|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120145720/https://www.npr.org/2015/07/18/424122249/theyre-no-1-u-s-wins-math-olympiad-for-first-time-in-21-years|dead-url=no}}</ref>、2016年<ref>{{Cite web|title=57th IMO 2016|url=https://www.imo-official.org/year_country_r.aspx?year=2016&column=total&order=desc|accessdate=2020-08-07|author=IMO|date=|format=|work=www.imo-official.org|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2018-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181125130156/https://www.imo-official.org/year_country_r.aspx?year=2016&column=total&order=desc|dead-url=no}}</ref>、2018年<ref>{{Cite web|title=59th International Mathematics Olympiad|url=https://www.imo-official.org/year_country_r.aspx?year=2018|accessdate=|author=|date=|last=|first=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430031402/https://www.imo-official.org/year_country_r.aspx?year=2018|archive-date=2021-04-30|access-date=2020-07-02|website=www.imo-official.org|dead-url=no}}</ref>及2019年赢得比赛<ref>{{Cite web|title=60th International Mathematics Olympiad|url=https://www.imo-official.org/year_country_r.aspx?year=2019|date=|last=|first=|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190925044747/https://www.imo-official.org/year_country_r.aspx?year=2019|archive-date=2019-09-25|access-date=2020-07-02|website=www.imo-official.org}}</ref>（2019 年美国与中国并列第一<ref>{{Cite web|title=60th IMO 2019|url=https://www.imo-official.org/year_country_r.aspx?year=2019&column=total&order=desc|accessdate=2020-08-07|author=IMO|date=|format=|work=www.imo-official.org|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410193148/https://www.imo-official.org/year_country_r.aspx?year=2019&column=total&order=desc|dead-url=no}}</ref>），是美国自1994年以来首次重新获胜<ref name="Strauss 2017">{{Cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/answer-sheet/wp/2016/07/18/u-s-students-win-prestigious-international-math-olympiad-for-second-straight-year/|title=U.S. students win prestigious International Math Olympiad — for second straight year|last=Strauss|first=Valerie|date=2016-07-18|work=[[Washington_Post|Washington Post]]|access-date=2017-12-28|issn=0190-8286|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027212125/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/answer-sheet/wp/2016/07/18/u-s-students-win-prestigious-international-math-olympiad-for-second-straight-year/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://fivethirtyeight.com/features/count-one-more-gold-for-the-u-s-in-math/|title=Count One More Gold For The U.S. — In Math|date=2016-08-25|work=[[FiveThirtyEight|FiveThirtyEight]]|access-date=2017-12-28|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225193502/https://fivethirtyeight.com/features/count-one-more-gold-for-the-u-s-in-math/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==生平==
罗博深曾于1999年参加国际数学奥林匹克竞赛，为美国赢得银牌<ref>{{Cite web|title=International Mathematical Olympiad|url=https://www.imo-official.org/participant_r.aspx?id=5589|website=www.imo-official.org|access-date=2018-03-25|archive-date=2021-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210425225129/http://www.imo-official.org/participant_r.aspx?id=5589|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，罗博深也开设课程，为[[威廉·羅威爾·普特南數學競賽|普特南数学竞赛]]培训学生，称为普特南研讨会（Putnam Seminar）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Carnegie Mellon University Putnam Seminar|url=http://www.math.cmu.edu/~ploh/2016-putnam.shtml|website=www.math.cmu.edu|access-date=2018-01-08|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119213429/https://www.math.cmu.edu/~ploh/2016-putnam.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。罗博深亦是教育网站 Expii 的创始人<ref name="Strauss 2017" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://wordplay.blogs.nytimes.com/2016/07/18/imo-2016/|title=U.S. Team Wins First Place at International Math Olympiad|last=[[Gary_Antonick|Antonick]]|first=Gary|date=2016-07-18|work=Wordplay Blog|access-date=2017-12-28|publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108132047/https://wordplay.blogs.nytimes.com/2016/07/18/imo-2016/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他还在卡内基梅隆大学教授离散数学和极限组合学课程<ref>{{Cite web|title=Teaching / CMU Putnam|url=http://www.math.cmu.edu/~ploh/teaching.shtml|access-date=2020-07-02|website=www.math.cmu.edu|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119220107/https://www.math.cmu.edu/~ploh/teaching.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==家庭==
罗博深是新加坡裔美国人，父母来自新加坡，祖籍分别是广州和汕头<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=我的故事（一）：童年的数学启蒙|url=https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/59416607|accessdate=2020-08-07|author=罗博深|date=|format=|work=知乎专栏|publisher=|language=zh}}</ref>。父亲罗伟贤是[[威斯康星大学麦迪逊分校|威斯康星大学麦迪逊分校]]统计学专业教授。母亲李月娥曾是新加坡高中数学老师<ref name=":0" />。他以 4.3 的平均成绩，毕业于[[加州理工學院|加州理工学院]]，并曾在[[普林斯顿大学|普林斯顿大学]]担任赫兹研究员（Hertz Fellow）。

==荣誉==
2019年获得[[美国青年科学家与工程师总统奖|美国青年科学家与工程师总统奖]]。<ref>[http://k.sina.com.cn/article_6468992679_18194fea701900hw3g.html 捷报| 罗博深教授获2019年美国青年科学家与工程师总统奖！] {{Wayback|url=http://k.sina.com.cn/article_6468992679_18194fea701900hw3g.html |date=20210420163501 }}，新浪新闻。</ref>

